<a href="https://iono.fm/e/644207">Content hosted by iono.fm</a> Note: Apologies for poor sound quality. Top five Chivas Venture finalist Sibusiso Pilingane of Kgosana Holdings fell in love with the bee industry and started a project that upskills communities in the keeping and raising of bees. The Chivas Venture competition gives away $1 million in no-strings funding, as well as expert coaching at the Chivas Venture Accelerator Programme, to social entrepreneurs who blend profit with purpose. The winner of the SA leg will be announced on January 23. Brought to you by Chivas Venture.